OL,3,CWoman with severe burns dies following
OL,4,Chouse fire in Gloucestershire
OL,6,FA woman in her 40s has died following
OL,7,Fa house fire in Gloucester.
OL,9,FEmergency services were sent to
OL,10,Freports of a fire on Attlebridge Way
OL,11,Fin Kingsway at around 5.25pm on
OL,12,FWednesday, 8 July.
OL,14,FThe woman was taken to Southmead
OL,15,FHospital in Bristol with severe burns
OL,16,Fbut died later that evening. Her death
OL,17,Fis not being treated as suspicious.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
