OL,3,CWoman with severe burns dies following
OL,4,Chouse fire in Gloucestershire
OL,6,FA cordon remains in place whilst
OL,7,Finvestigations from Gloucestershire
OL,8,FPolice and Gloucestershire Fire and
OL,9,FRescue Service are underway.
OL,11,FActing Detective Inspector Sophie
OL,12,FDawkins said: "Our thoughts are with
OL,13,Fthe woman's family and with all those
OL,14,Fwho have been impacted by this sad
OL,15,Fincident.
OL,17,F"I would like to take the time to
OL,18,Fthank the members of the public who
OL,19,Fassisted in attempting to save the
OL,20,Fwoman before emergency services
OL,21,Farrived.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
