OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1783702081
OL,3,CWoman with severe burns dies following
OL,4,Chouse fire in Gloucestershire
OL,6,F"My thanks also go to the first
OL,7,Fresponders and those within the
OL,8,Femergency services who continue their
OL,9,Fwork at the scene."
OL,11,FOfficers are still working at the
OL,12,Fscene to establish what happened.
